So as a fighter
test pilot, you live

00:02:10.020 --> 00:02:11.980
in the world of being
a fighter pilot,

00:02:11.980 --> 00:02:14.070
but you also have the
ability to understand Matlab

00:02:14.070 --> 00:02:17.040
