that's there is it's

00:03:19.350 --> 00:03:23.250
just like-- look, by the
way, warning to the class,

00:03:23.250 --> 00:03:26.460
I talk a lot in terms of movies,
Game of Thrones, or whatever,

00:03:26.460 --> 00:03:29.010
television shows and sports
