00:03:49.020 --> 00:03:51.900
That same kind of
discernment that you

00:03:51.900 --> 00:03:54.630
have when you're shopping
for cars, this airplane

00:03:54.630 --> 00:03:56.160
is a couple hundred
million dollars.

